a]]\n\n===Discovery===\n* ''[[Angel (2009 film)|Angel]]'' by [[Margreth Olin]]\n* ''[[Applause]]'' by [[Martin Pieter Zandvliet]]\n* ''[[Bare Essence of Life]]'' by [[Satoko Yokohama]]\n* ''[[Beautiful Kate]]'' by [[Rachel Ward]]\n* ''[[A Brand New Life (2009 film)|A Brand New Life]]'' by [[Ounie Lecomte]]\n* ''[[The Day Will Come (2009 film)|The Day Will Come]]'' by [[Susanne Schneider]]\n* ''[[The Disappearance of Alice Creed]]'' by [[J Blakeson]]\n* ''[[Eamon (film)|Eamon]]'' by [[Margaret Corkery]]\n* ''[[Everyday is a Holiday]]'' by [[Dima El-Horr]]\n* ''[[Five Hours from Paris]]'' by [[Leon Pruddovsky]]\n* ''[[Gigante (film)|Gigante]]'' by [[Adri\u00e1n Biniez]]\n* ''[[The Happiest Girl in the World]]'' by [[Radu Jude]]\n* ''[[Heliopolis (film)|Heliopolis]]'' by [[Ahmad Abdalla]]\n* ''[[Le Jour Ou Dieu Est Parti en Voyage]]'' by [[Philippe van Leeuw]]\n* ''[[Kelin]]'' by [[Ermek Tursunov]]\n* ''[[Last Ride (film)|Last Ride]]'' by [[Glendyn Ivin]]\n* ''[[The Man Beyond the Bridge]]'' by [[Laxmikant Shetgaonkar]]\n* ''[[My Dog Tulip]]'' by [[Paul Fierlinger]] and [[Sandra Fierlinger]]\n* ''[[My Tehran for Sale]]'' by [[Granaz Moussavi]]\n* ''[[Northless]]'' by [[Rigoberto Perezcano]]\n* ''[[La Pivellina]]'' by [[Tizza Covi]] and [[Rainer Frimmel]]\n* ''[[Samson and Delilah (2009 film)|Samson and Delilah]]'' by [[Warwick Thornton]]\n* ''[[Shirley Adams]]'' by [[Oliver Hermanus]]\n* ''[[Should I Really Do It?]]'' by [[Ismail Necmi]]\n* ''[[La Soga]]'' by [[Josh Crook]]\n* ''[[Toad's Oil]]'' by [[K\u014dji Yakusho]]\n* ''[[Together (2009 film)|Together]]'' by [[Matias Armand Jordal]]\n* ''[[The Unloved]]'' by [[Samantha Morton]]\n\n===Future Projections===\n* ''[[The Butcher's Shop]]'' by [[Philip Haas]]\n* ''[[Cathedral]]'' by [[Marco Brambilla]]\n* ''[[The Death of Tom]]'' by [[Glenn Ligon]]\n* ''[[I'm Feeling Lucky]]'' by [[Samuel Chow]]\n* ''[[Teenager Hamlet 2006]]'' by [[Margaux Williamson]]\n* ''[[Utopia Suite]]'' by [[Clive Holden]]\n* ''[[When the Gods Came Down to Earth]]'' by [[Srinivas Krishna]]\n\n===Gala Presentations===\n* ''[[Agora (film)|Agora]]'' by [[Alejandro Amenabar]]\n* ''[[Chloe (film)|Chloe]]'' by [[Atom Egoyan]]\n* ''[[Coco Chanel and Igor Stravinsky]]'' by [[Jan Kounen]]\n* ''[[Cooking with Stella]]'' by [[Dilip Mehta]]\n* ''[[Creation (2009 film)|Creation]]'' by [[Jon Amiel]]\n* ''[[The Damned United]]'' by [[Tom Hooper (director)|Tom Hooper]]\n* ''[[Dil Bole Hadippa]]'' by [[Anurag Singh (director)|Anurag Singh]]\n* ''[[Dorian Gray (2009 film)|Dorian Gray]]'' by [[Oliver Parker]]\n* ''[[Get Low (film)|Get Low]]'' by [[Aaron Schneider]]\n* ''[[I, Don Giovanni]]'' by [[Carlos Saura]]\n* ''[[The Imaginarium of Doctor Parnassus]]'' by [[Terry Gilliam]]\n* ''[[Max Manus (film)|Max Manus]]'' by [[Espen Sandberg]] and [[Joachim Roenning]]\n* ''[[The Men Who Stare at Goats (film)|The Men Who Stare at Goats]]'' by [[Grant Heslov]]\n* ''[[Micmacs (film)|Micmacs]]'' by [[Jean-Pierre Jeunet]]''\n* ''[[Mother and Child (2009 film)|Mother and Child]]'' by [[Rodrigo Garc\u00eda (director)|Rodrigo Garc\u00eda]]\n* ''[[The Other Woman (2009 film)|The Other Woman]]'' by [[Don Roos]]\n* ''[[Phantom Pain]]'' by [[Matthias Emcke]]\n* ''[[Precious (film)|Precious]]'' by [[Lee Daniels]]\n* ''[[The Private Lives of Pippa Lee]]'' by [[Rebecca Miller]]\n* ''[[What's Your Raashee?]]'' by [[Ashutosh Gowariker]]\n* ''[[The Young Victoria]]'' by [[Jean-Marc Vall\u00e9e]]\n\n===Masters===\n* ''[[Air Doll]]'' by [[Hirokazu Kore-eda]]\n* ''[[La Donation]]'' by [[Bernard Emond]]\n* ''[[Eccentricities of a Blonde-haired Girl]]'' by [[Manoel de Oliveira]]\n* ''[[Wild Grass|Les Herbes folles]]'' by [[Alain Resnais]]\n* ''[[Janala]]'' by [[Buddhadeb Dasgupta]]\n* ''[[Antichrist]]'' by [[Lars von Trier]]\n\n===Midnight Madness<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ultra8.ca/content2/mmhistory.html|title=History of the Toronto International Film Festival's MIDNIGHT MADNESS Programme|accessdate=October 19, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019173241/http://www.ultra8.ca/content2/mmhistory.html|archive-date=2013-10-19|url-status=dead|df=}}</ref>===\n* ''[[Bitch Slap]]'' by [[Rick Jacobson]]\n* ''[[Daybreakers]]'' by [[Michael Spierig]] and [[Peter Spierig]]\n* ''[[Survival of the Dead]]'' by [[George A. Romero]]\n* ''[[Jennifer's Body]]'' by [[Karyn Kusama]]\n* ''[[The Loved Ones (film)|The Loved Ones]]'' by [[Sean Byrne (director)|Sean Byrne]]\n* ''[[Ong Bak 2]]'' by [[Tony Jaa]] and [[Panna Rittikrai]]\n* ''[[REC 2|[REC 2]]]'' by [[Jaume Balaguer\u00f3]] and [[Paco Plaza]]\n* ''[[Solomon Kane (film)|Solomon Kane]]'' by [[Michael J. Bassett]]\n* ''[[Symbol]]'' by [[Hitoshi Matsumoto]]\n* ''[[A Town Called Panic]]'' by [[St\u00e9phane Aubier]] and [[Vincent Patar]]\n\n===Reel to Reel===\n* ''[[The Art of the Steal (2009 film)|The Art of the Steal]]'' by [[Don Argott]]\n* ''[[Bassidji]]'' by [[Mehran Tamadon]]\n* ''[[Cleanflix]]'' by Andrew James and [[Joshua Ligairi]]\n* ''[[Collapse (film)|Collapse]]'' by [[Chris Smith (filmmaker)|Chris Smith]]\n* ''[[Colony]]'' by [[Carter Gunn]] and [[Ross McDonnell]]\n* ''[[Genius Within: The Inner Life of Glenn Gould]]'' by [[Peter Raymont]] and [[Michele Hozer]]\n* ''[[Google Baby]]'' by [[Zippi Brand Frank]]\n* ''[[How to Fold a Flag]]'' by [[Michael Tucker (director)|Michael Tucker]] and [[Petra Epperlein]]\n* ''[[L' Enfer de Henri-Georges Clouzot]]'' by [[Serge Bromberg]] and [[Ruxandra Medrea]]\n* ''[[The Most Dangerous Man in America: Daniel Ellsberg and the Pentagon Papers]]'' by [[Judith Ehrlich]] and [[Rick Goldsmith]]\n* ''[[Petropolis: Aerial Perspectives on the Alberta Tar Sands]]'' by [[Peter Mettler]]\n* ''[[Presumed Guilty (2009 film)|Presumed Guilty]]'' by [[Roberto Hern\u00e1ndez (filmmaker)|Roberto Hern\u00e1ndez]] and [[Geoffrey Smith (filmmaker)|Geoffrey Smith]]\n* ''[[Reel Injun]]'' by [[Neil Diamond (filmmaker)|Neil Diamond]]\n* ''[[Schmatta: Rags to Riches to Rags]]'' by [[Marc Levin]]\n* ''[[Snowblind (film)|Snowblind]]'' by [[Vikram Jayanti]]\n* ''[[Stolen documentary|''Stolen'']]'' by [[Violeta Ayala]] and [[Dan Fallshaw]]\n* ''[[The Topp Twins]]'' by [[Leanne Pooley]]\n* ''[[Videocracy (film)|Videocracy]]'' by [[Erik Gandini]]\n\n===Vanguard===\n* ''[[Accident (2009 film)|Accident]]'' by [[Soi Cheang]]\n* ''[[The Ape (2009 film)|The Ape]]'' by [[Jesper Ganslandt]]\n* ''[[Bunny and the Bull]]'' by [[Paul King (director)|Paul King]]\n* ''[[Carcasses (film)|Carcasses]]'' by [[Denis C\u00f4t\u00e9]]\n* ''[[The Dirty Saints]]'' by [[Luis Ortega (film director)|Luis Ortega]]\n* ''[[Enter the Void]]'' by [[Gaspar No\u00e9]]\n* ''[[Fish Tank (film)|Fish Tank]]'' by [[Andrea Arnold]]\n* ''[[Hipsters (film)|Hipsters]]'' by [[Valery Todorovsky]]\n* ''[[The Misfortunates]]'' by [[Felix Van Groeningen]]\n* ''[[Leslie, My Name Is Evil]]'' by [[Reginald Harkema]]\n* ''[[My Queen Karo]]'' by [[Doroth\u00e9e van den Berghe]]\n* ''[[Spring Fever (2009 film)|Spring Fever]]'' by [[Lou Ye]]\n* ''[[The White Stripes Under Great White Northern Lights]]'' by [[Emmett Malloy]]\n\n===Visions===\n* ''[[Between Two Worlds (2009 film)|Between Two Worlds]]'' by [[Vimukthi Jayasundara]]\n* ''[[Face (2009 film)|Face]]'' by [[Tsai Ming-liang]]\n* ''[[Gaia (film)|Gaia]]'' by [[Jason Lehel]]\n* ''[[Hiroshima]]'' by [[Pablo Stoll]]\n* ''[[Independencia (film)|Independencia]]'' by [[Raya Martin]]\n* ''[[I Am Love (film)|I Am Love]]'' by [[Luca Guadagnino]]\n* ''[[Irene (2009 film)|Irene]]'' by [[Alain Cavalier]]\n* ''[[Karaoke]]'' by [[Chris Chong]]\n* ''[[Lebanon (2009 film)|Lebanon]]'' by [[Samuel Maoz]]\n* ''[[Nymph (2009 film)|Nymph]]'' by [[Pen-Ek Ratanaruang]]\n* ''[[To Die Like a Man]]'' by [[Jo\u00e3o Pedro Rodrigues]]\n* ''[[To the Sea]]'' [[Pedro Gonz\u00e1lez-Rubio]]\n* ''[[Trash Humpers]]'' by [[Harmony Korine]]\n\n===Short Cuts===\n* ''5 Dysfunctional People in a Car'', [[Pat Mills (director)|Pat Mills]]\n* ''75 El Camino'', Sami Khan\n* ''[[The Armoire]]'', [[Jamie Travis]]\n* ''Big Head, Dylan Akio Smith \n* 