irector)|He Ping]]\n* ''[[Whip It!]]'' by [[Drew Barrymore]]\n* ''[[Women Without Men (2009 film)|Women Without Men]]'' by [[Shirin Neshat]]\n* ''[[Youth in Revolt (film)|Youth in Revolt]]'' by [[Miguel Arteta]]\n\n===City to City===\n* ''[[Bena (film)|Bena]]'' by [[Niv Klainer]]\n* ''[[Blaumilch Canal|Big Dig]]'' by [[Ephraim Kishon|Efraim Kishon]]\n* ''[[Big Eyes]]'' by [[Uri Zohar]]\n* ''[[The Bubble (2006 film)|The Bubble]]'' by [[Eytan Fox]]\n* ''[[A History of Israeli Cinema - Part 1]]'' by [[Raphael Nadjari]]\t\t\n* ''[[A History of Israeli Cinema - Part 2]]'' by [[Raphael Nadjari]]\n* ''[[Jaffa (2009 film)|Jaffa]]'' by [[Keren Yedaya]]\n* ''[[Kirot]]'' by [[Danny Lerner]]\n* ''[[Life According to Agfa]]'' by [[Assi Dayan]]\n* ''[[Phobidilia]]'' by [[Yoav Paz]] and [[Doron Paz]]\n\n===Contemporary World Cinema===\n* ''[[Beyond the Circle]]'' by [[Golam Rabbany]]\n* ''[[Blessed (2009 film)|Blessed]]'' by [[Ana Kokkinos]]\n* ''[[Cole (film)|Cole]]'' by [[Carl Bessai]]\n* ''[[Down for Life (film)|Down for Life]]'' by [[Alan Jacobs (filmmaker)|Alan Jacobs]]\n* ''[[Excited (film)|Excited]]'' by [[Bruce Sweeney]]\n* ''[[Eyes Wide Open (2009 film)|Eyes Wide Open]]'' by [[Haim Tabakman]]\n* ''[[Giulia Doesn\u2019t Date at Night]]'' by [[Giuseppe Piccioni]]\n* ''[[A Gun to the Head]]'' by [[Blaine Thurier]]\n* ''[[Heiran]]'' by [[Shalizeh Arefpour]]\n* ''[[High Life (2009 film)|High Life]]'' by [[Gary Yates (director)|Gary Yates]]\n* ''[[The House of Branching Love]]'' by [[Mika Kaurism\u00e4ki]]\n* ''[[Huacho]]'' by [[Alejandro Fern\u00e1ndez Alemendras]]\n* ''[[Jean Charles (film)|Jean Charles]]'' by [[Henrique Goldman]]\n* ''[[Like You Know It All]]'' by [[Hong Sang-soo|Hong Sangsoo]]\n* ''[[Lourdes (film)|Lourdes]]'' by [[Jessica Hausner]]\n* ''[[Men on the Bridge]]'' by [[Asli \u00d6zge]]\n* ''[[My Year Without Sex (film)|My Year Without Sex]]'' by [[Sarah Watt]]\n* ''[[Passenger Side]]'' by [[Matthew Bissonnette]]\n* ''[[Police, Adjective]]'' by [[Corneliu Porum